The reserved room '%2$s' for your '%3$s' meeting scheduled at %4$s has been released because no participants have checked in to the room.

We noticed that you have not checked in to this meeting %5$s consecutive times. We will permanently remove your reserved room for recurring meetings with no participant check-in after %6$s consecutive meeting occurrences.

"

Zoom Rooms require a tablet or iPad that is connected to a Mac or PC running the Zoom Rooms software in order to manage meetings. Install and run the software from https://zoom.us/download under Zoom Rooms for Conference Rooms to find the 6-character code.

After you pair the devices, sign in or click the link to enter Activation Code. Locate or generate the activation code on https://zoom.us/location in room settings.

For Scheduling Display Only rooms, simply sign in without pairing and select the desired room.

For additional help, contact Zoom Technical Support at support@zoom.us
